title: Fighting Is Magic Collection v2
description:
Unpack and play, also works with Wine.
     
1.leaked - first leaked version, not modded and without AI.
2.evostorm - modification by Evost0rm: modded leaked version with AI and new stages.
3.iwanabrawl - mod by Iwanabrawl: added Fluttershy (static sprite) and Rainbow Dash, better AI, boss, new stages, rebalancing, support network game.
4.tribute - better RD sptires, playable Fluttershy, new menus and network client. Without boss in this version, perhaps because another developer.
